akka.routing

Class FromConfig$

  • java.lang.Object
    • akka.routing.FromConfig
      • akka.routing.FromConfig$
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Pool, RouterConfig, java.io.Serializable, scala.Equals, scala.Product

    public class FromConfig$
extends FromConfig
implements scala.Product, scala.Serializable
    Wraps a Props to mark the actor as externally configurable to be used with a router. If a Props is not wrapped with FromConfig then the actor will ignore the router part of the deployment section in the configuration.
    See Also:
